{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01X9zeQbvauK3o8TXiMjNeuh","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Sample Specification\n2\t\n3\tThis document is a minimal Source Specs fixture for verifying spec-anchor end-to-end behavior in a real LLM + Qdrant environment.\n4\t\n5\t## Authentication\n6\t\n7\tUsers authenticate with an email address and a password. A successful login establishes a session that expires after 24 hours of inactivity. The login endpoint rate-limits to 5 attempts per minute per remote IP. Multi-factor authentication is required for administrator accounts; service accounts are exempt.\n8\t\n9\t## Authorization\n10\t\n11\tAdmin users may read, create, update, and delete any resource. Regular users may read and update only resources they own. Service accounts authenticate with API keys and never see the login UI.\n12\t\n13\t## Session Termination\n14\t\n15\tLogging out invalidates the current session immediately. Sessions that exceed the 24-hour inactivity window are automatically purged by a background sweep that runs every five minutes.\n16\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"293a00a8-6688-4c5c-a826-2a7374dd1b52","uuid":"0c631942-70d1-4908-ad63-1e26a1fea6a8","timestamp":"2026-05-23T00:34:35.722Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/docs/spec/sample.md","content":"# Sample Specification\n\nThis document is a minimal Source Specs fixture for verifying spec-anchor end-to-end behavior in a real LLM + Qdrant environment.\n\n## Authentication\n\nUsers authenticate with an email address and a password. A successful login establishes a session that expires after 24 hours of inactivity. The login endpoint rate-limits to 5 attempts per minute per remote IP. Multi-factor authentication is required for administrator accounts; service accounts are exempt.\n\n## Authorization\n\nAdmin users may read, create, update, and delete any resource. Regular users may read and update only resources they own. Service accounts authenticate with API keys and never see the login UI.\n\n## Session Termination\n\nLogging out invalidates the current session immediately. Sessions that exceed the 24-hour inactivity window are automatically purged by a background sweep that runs every five minutes.\n","numLines":16,"startLine":1,"totalLines":16}}}
